==English==

===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰeh₂|id=speak}}
Recorded since 1656; from {{der|en|grc|εὐφημισμός}}, from {{m|grc|εὐφημίζω}}, from {{m|grc|εὔφημος||uttering sound of good omen, abstaining from inauspicious words}}, from {{m|grc|εὖ||well}} + {{m|grc|φήμη||a voice, a prophetic voice, rumor, talk}}, from {{m|grc|φάναι||to speak, say}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|yoo͞'fə-mĭz"(ə)m}}, {{IPA|/ˈjuː.fəˌmɪ.z(ə)m/|lang=en}}
